<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.7">
<l>uṇṇā tuṟaṅkā tolikaṭalai yūṭaṟuttup</l>
<l>peṇṇākkai yāppuṇṭu tāmuṟṟa pētellām,</l>
<l>tiṇṇār matiḷcūḻ tiruvaraṅkac celvaṉār</l>
<l>eṇṇātē tammuṭaiya naṉmaikaḷē yeṇṇuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not eating, nor sleeping [but] cutting through the roaring sea,</l>
<l>The Wealthy Man from Śrīraṅgam surrounded by firm ramparts</l>
<l>Did not remember the delirium that He got feeling affection for the woman’s body (Sītā)</l>
<l>[but] will only think [now] of His virtues!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
